<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>회원가입 - AXIO</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    .invite-field { position: relative; }
    .invite-field input { padding-right: 36px; }
    .invite-icon {
      position: absolute; right: 12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-size: 16px; pointer-events: none;
    }
    .code-hint {
      font-size: 11px; color: var(--text2); margin-top: 4px;
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px; padding: 6px 10px; line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="auth-wrap">
  <div class="auth-card">
    <div class="auth-logo">AXIO</div>
    <div class="auth-sub">웹 취약점 모의훈련 센터</div>

    <% if (error) { %>
    <div class="alert alert-error"><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>
    <% if (success) { %>
    <div class="alert alert-success"><%= success %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="POST" action="/register">
      <!-- 초대 코드 필드 (최상단 배치) -->
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>🎫 초대 코드 <span style="color:var(--red)">*</span></label>
        <div class="invite-field">
          <input type="text" name="invite_code" placeholder="AXIO-XXXX-XXXX" autocomplete="off" style="font-family:monospace;letter-spacing:1px">
          <span class="invite-icon">🔑</span>
        </div>
        <div class="code-hint">
          훈련 주관자에게 초대 코드를 받아 입력하세요.<br>
          <strong>데모 코드:</strong> <code>AXIO-TRAIN-2024</code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="divider" style="margin:16px 0"></div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>아이디</label>
        <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="아이디">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>비밀번호 <span class="vuln-tag">평문 저장</span></label>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호 (그대로 저장됩니다)">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>이메일</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="이메일 (선택)">
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">훈련 시작하기</button>
    </form>

    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div style="text-align:center;color:var(--text2);font-size:13px">
      이미 계정이 있으신가요? <a href="/login">로그인</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
